"""
Calculator

A simple calculator program written in Python3, that serves the 4 basic arithemtic operations - Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, Division. This script is written only for learning purposes and is very good practice for python language beginners to learn using this program.

Author : Anirudha Taliyan (https://github.com/anirudhataliyan/)
